				<wikidot:authorName>440 Hertz</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1249440</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Glad you liked the development! It was tough deciding whether to do a &quot;two levels of clearance&quot; reveal, but in the end I really liked the feeling of a deliberate controlled cognitive dissonance. Like in the ConProcs with the &quot;factual accuracy is optional (for instance, the entity was keter but we changed our mind since it's a lame doodoohead)&quot; thing.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
