					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10211745#post-4144367</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10211745/scp-3638#post-4144367</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 06 Feb 2019 23:45:48 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>440 Hertz</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1249440</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Thesis: there's something inherently scary about humor. It's a refuge, a desperate charade, a coping mechanism in the face of a meaningless unjust cold universe and a life full of daily discomfort and hardships. Antithesis: there's something inherently <em>epic</em> about <em>memes</em>. This is my humble synthesis.</p> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4483018&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1549496748" alt="TheMightyMcB" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4483018)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/themightymcb" >TheMightyMcB</a></span> who helped so much in all stages he's practically a co-author, to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/waxwing-one" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4917178&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1549496748" alt="Waxwing-one" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4917178)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/waxwing-one" >Waxwing-one</a></span> for their great insights (notably coming up with the idea of a compilation of doodles), and to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1549496748" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" >DarkStuff</a></span> for his very helpful critique!</p> <p>I'm the author of all images.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
